TY  - JOUR
T1  - A Data Disclosure Policy for Count Data Based on the COM-Poisson Distribution
AU  - Kadane, Joseph B.
AU  - Krishnan, Ramayya
AU  - Shmueli, Galit
Y1  - 2006/10/01
PY  - 2006
DA  - 2006/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.1060.0562
